    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，我先确认一下结构：第一个section是\"Create/Update Event\"，里面放\"Save Event\"节点，它触发Scheduler。然后第二个section专门处理条件判断对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Create/Update Event",
        "Save Event",
        "Scheduler",
        "Evaluate Conditions"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，第二个section叫\"Evaluate Conditions\"，要判断四个条件：有没有参会者、是否24小时内开始、是否1小时内开始、还是更远的将来。每个条件对应不同的调度任务。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Evaluate Conditions",
        "Has attendees?",
        "Starts in 24h?",
        "Starts in 1h?",
        "Starts in future?"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我把条件判断部分画好了。现在画第三个section\"Delivery\"，提醒任务执行时先加载确认参加的参会者，然后对每个参会者发送通知。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Delivery",
        "Reminder job runs",
        "going attendees"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "发送通知那里要说明技术方案：用ActionCable实时推送加上邮件，而且要批量处理，避免一下子发太多请求。节点名可以叫\"Noticed\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "For each attendee",
        "Noticed",
        "ActionCable",
        "Email",
        "batched"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下，最后一个节点我这样写：\"For each attendee : Noticed = ActionCable + Email (batched)\"，这样把循环逻辑和技术栈都表达清楚了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "For each attendee",
        "Noticed",
        "ActionCable",
        "Email",
